data.description: You won’t want to miss out on this absolute gem in established Oakcrest - less than 5 minutes to vibrant and quaint Main St. This stunning 3 bedroom brick home eagerly awaits your personal touches with its hardwood floors & fresh paint throughout. The generous kitchen has ample counter space & cabinets for storage. The front living room teems with natural light from the large mid-century modern style windows. Gorgeous mature trees line the front yard providing tranquility and privacy. The backyard is spacious and fenced and begging for that outdoor living for you while the kids or pups run free. The oversized carport is a bonus and could easily be replaced with an even larger garage with living space above for the future. New HVAC (Summer 2023) New plumbing fixtures & toilet (Fall 2023) and fiber optic ready! Walk to the local Farmer’s Market. 10 min drive to the White Water Center & Belmont Abbey College. 20 min to airport. 30 min to Charlotte center city.  Do NOT wait on this one!
